   Intricate drama thriller series which tracks five 24-hour periods
   following the abduction of a beautiful young mother. The
   disappearance of Leanne and Rosie is now all over the headlines.
   Press officer Defne Topcu tries to cajole both the family and DCI
   Barclay into attending the first major press conference of the
   enquiry. But husband Matt is refusing to attend and Barclay seems
   at best indifferent. It&#039;s left to Leanne&#039;s mother, Barbara, to
   make an emotional appeal for Leanne&#039;s return.
